Babo is the leader of the slaves in "Benito Cereno." Babo led the slave revolt against the sailors, taking over theSan Dominick.For most of "Benito Cereno," Babo masquerades as Cereno's servant. However, he is actually there to keep an eye on Cereno and to make sure that Cereno doesn't betray Babo and the slaves to Captain Delano. Babo is small, but he is wily and intelligent.